description:
Poise Impressa Bladder Supports are a revolutionary incontinence product worn internally to help stop bladder leaks before they happen. Designed for women with urinary incontinence who laugh, cough, sneeze, run or swim- known as Stress Urinary Incontinence- Impressa Bladder Supports are for you! Safe, effective and easy-to-use, Impressa comes in three different sizes to fit each woman's unique internal shape. The Impressa Sizing Kit includes all three sizes, two of each. Start with Size 1 and work your way up to find the most comfortable fit and best performance. Then, purchase additional Poise Impressa Bladder Supports in your specific size: Size 1 (10ct.), Size 2 (10ct.) or Size 3 (10ct.).

Poise Impressa is the first over-the-counter, pessary device approved by the FDA and Health Canada, and it is gynecologist-tested. The Impressa Bladder Support is inserted like a tampon to gently lift and support the urethra to help stop bladder leakage, while allowing you to use the bathroom as usual. Poise Impressa can be worn for up to 12 hours within a 24-hour period. Help stop your incontinence and bladder leaks with Impressa Bladder Supports. Poise Impressa Bladder Supports are available online and in stores without a prescription and are an FSA-eligible product (applicable only in the U.S.).
title: Poise Bladder Supports Sizing Kit: 1,2,3 - 6ct

bullets: The Poise Impressa Bladder Support Sizing Kit contains Size 1, Size 2 and Size 3 bladder supports (two of each size)
Worn internally, Impressa gently lifts and supports the urethra to help stop bladder leaks associated with Stress Urinary Incontinence (SUI)
Small, non-absorbent support inserts easily into the vagina, like a tampon, and may be worn for up to 12 hours in a 24-hour period
FDA- and Health Canada-approved, gynecologist-tested and FSA-eligible (applicable only in the U.S.)
A comfortable, disposable incontinence solution that can eliminate the need for bulky, bladder control pads
